              </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                    
                    <p 
  align=left><br>
                      <font size="2" face="georgia"><strong><font color="#006600" face="Verdana">CONSUMPTION 
                      SUGGESTIONS: PURA VITTA NONI JUICE</font></strong></font></p>
                    <p 
  align=justify><font size="2" face="Verdana">The Pura Vitta Noni Juice has a 
                      high Noni fruit percentage in its formula, and it is mixed 
                      with a small quantity of grape juice for better taste. Pura 
                      Vitta Noni juice is completely natural.<strong><br>
                      <br>
                      <br>
                      ADULTS<br>
                      </strong>2 oz in the morning on an empty stomach. 2 oz 30 
                      minutes before dinner.<strong><br>
                      <br>
                      CHILDREN<br>
                      </strong>1 oz a day, preferably in the morning, on an empty 
                      stomach.</font></p>
                    <p align="left">&nbsp;</p>
                    <p align="center"><font size="2" face="Verdana">The suggestions 
                      above could vary depending on body mass. Always consult 
                      your doctor.</font></p>
